<i>Posted by Nanashi on 04-09-2001 03:50 PM:</i>

<p><b> Diff system</b></p>

<p>On guild raids we often use the system of assigning numbers to a player who is eligible for an item, then rolling on a very small range, i.e:<br>
<br>
1 - Fahren<br>
2 - Nanashi<br>
3 - Dyvette<br>
4 - Aalavar<br>
<br>
Then a group leader does /random 1-4 to see who gets it. Depending on eligibility of people for the item, numbers assigned will always change.<FONT face="arial, helvetica" size="2"><br>
